  "detailed_description": "Mirror Drop is a psychedelic 3D puzzle game where you maneuver a reflective sphere in a world full of mirrors, over-saturated colors, and infinities. Each level contains three puzzles and a hidden exit, set against 100% raytraced alien geometry.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>25 levels<br></li><li>3+ hours of content<br></li><li>3 save slots (auto-saves after each level)</li></ul>",
